    <description>Record-Triggered Flow runs on create or update of an OS_Candidate_Address__c record. If the status is &apos;Search in Progress&apos; and has changed, it calls the &apos;OS Find and Cleanse&apos; Apex action to search for an address. It updates the record with matched details or sets the status to &apos;Search Failed&apos; on error, and checks for duplicates to update the status appropriately.</description>
